      "text": "[https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41Mz6JuPZVL._SX354_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E4%BE%8B%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E5%AD%A6%E3%81%B6-%E5%A4%9A%E6%A7%98%E4%BD%93-%E8%97%A4%E5%B2%A1-%E6%95%A6/dp/4785315717/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&qid=&sr=]",
